lines.text: Oh, so you rob from the rich, and give to the poor?
No, I rob from the rich, and pretty much keep it for myself.
I'll have my revenge... and Deathstalker too!
Deathstalker? Is that your first name or your last name?
Ordinarily I don't mind seeing a woman get a good beating, if she deserves it, but this doesn't look like much of a contest to me.
You have to get up pretty early in the morning to catch the prince of thieves.
IT IS EARLY IN THE MORNING!
And last but not least a real find, Buddy 'Footstool' Laroza, only recently dismissed by Ivan the Terrible for excessive brutality
